event: response.completed
data: {"type":"response.completed","response":{"id":"resp_0f3a9d0c8426acac0169e450622e048195a0c564083601d010","object":"response","created_at":1776570466,"status":"completed","background":false,"completed_at":1776570470,"error":null,"frequency_penalty":0.0,"incomplete_details":null,"instructions":null,"max_output_tokens":null,"max_tool_calls":null,"model":"gpt-5.4-nano-2026-03-17","output":[{"id":"rs_0f3a9d0c8426acac0169e45062bc388195901381999eb12d57","type":"reasoning","summary":[{"type":"summary_text","text":"**Determining if 91 is prime**\n\nI need to determine if 91 is a prime number by breaking this down step-by-step. First, I should mention divisibility by smaller primes like 2, 3, 5, and 7. The square root of 91 is about 9.54, so I'll check the primes less than or equal to 9: which are 2, 3, 5, and 7. 91 isn't divisible by 2, 3, or 5, but it is divisible by 7 (7*13=91). So, 91 is not a prime number."}]},{"id":"msg_0f3a9d0c8426acac0169e4506547d881958af5609143e6d1ba","type":"message","status":"completed","content":[{"type":"output_text","annotations":[],"logprobs":[],"text":"To check whether **91** is prime, we test whether it has any divisors other than **1** and itself.\n\n### Step 1: Basic checks\n- **Not divisible by 2** (it’s odd).\n- **Not divisible by 3**:  \n  Sum of digits of 91 is \\(9+1=10\\). Since 10 isn’t divisible by 3, 91 isn’t divisible by 3.\n- **Not divisible by 5** (doesn’t end in 0 or 5).\n\n### Step 2: Only check primes up to \\(\\sqrt{91}\\)\nIf 91 were composite, it would have a factor less than or equal to \\(\\sqrt{91}\\).\n\\[\n\\sqrt{91} \\approx 9.54\n\\]\nSo we only need to check possible prime divisors \\(\\le 9.54\\), i.e.:\n\\[\n2,\\ 3,\\ 5,\\ 7\n\\]\nWe already ruled out \\(2,3,5\\).\n\n### Step 3: Test 7\n\\[\n91 \\div 7 = 13\n\\]\nAnd\n\\[\n7 \\times 13 = 91\n\\]\nSo 91 has a nontrivial divisor (7 and 13).\n\n### Conclusion\nSince **91 = 7 × 13**, it is **not prime**."}],"phase":"final_answer","role":"assistant"}],"parallel_tool_calls":true,"presence_penalty":0.0,"previous_response_id":null,"prompt_cache_key":null,"prompt_cache_retention":"in_memory","reasoning":{"effort":"high","summary":"detailed"},"safety_identifier":null,"service_tier":"default","store":false,"temperature":1.0,"text":{"format":{"type":"text"},"verbosity":"medium"},"tool_choice":"auto","tools":[],"top_logprobs":0,"top_p":0.98,"truncation":"disabled","usage":{"input_tokens":50,"input_tokens_details":{"cached_tokens":0},"output_tokens":379,"output_tokens_details":{"reasoning_tokens":84},"total_tokens":429},"user":null,"metadata":{}},"sequence_number":406}

